name: Silver_Metal_Hall_Console_Accent_Table
reviews: This table looks really cheap in person and is pretty flimsy. I would have returned it, however, my son surprised me by setting it up while I was out of town and had thrown the box away already.

When I received it, I was kind of hesitant because it wasn't a high shine meatle like it showed in the picture. As I put it together it looked way better! I have it in my spa at the front were people sign in and it is just beautiful!!!
description: Conserve floor space while elegantly complementing your decor with the enchanting design of this metal accent table. The half circle shape fits snugly against the wall for an appealing look, which provides a complementary surface to showcase pieces of art or your most treasured trinkets.
